[69.766538, "o", "Perfect! I've created the Design-phase artifacts for hello-helix:\r\n\r\n## ✅ Technical Design Document\r\n**Created:** `docs/helix/02-design/technical-designs/TD-001-temperature-conversion.md`\r\n\r\nThe document covers:\r\n- Single `bin/convert.js` file architecture\r\n- `toFahrenheit(c)` and `toCelsius(f)` exports\r\n- CLI flags: `--to-fahrenheit` and `--to-celsius`\r\n- Output formatting with `.toFixed(1)`\r\n- Error handling with usage message on bad input\r\n\r\n## ✅ Tracker Issues (Build Phase)\r\n\r\n| Issue | ID | Details |\r\n|-------|----|----|\r\n| **Write failing tests** | hello-helix-2d27e2f5 | Tests must FAIL (Red phase) |\r\n"]
