[72.77264, "o", "# TD-001: Temperature Conversion Module\r\n\r\n## Overview\r\nTechnical design for the temperature conversion module, a lightweight utility for converting between Celsius and Fahrenheit scales.\r\n\r\n## Architecture\r\n- **Single file**: `bin/convert.js`\r\n- **Runtime**: Node.js\r\n- **Dependencies**: None (stdlib only)\r\n\r\n## Exports\r\n\r\n### `toFahrenheit(celsius)`\r\nConverts a Celsius temperature to Fahrenheit.\r\n\r\n**Parameters:**\r\n- `celsius` (number): Temperature in Celsius\r\n\r\n**Returns:** \r\n- (number): Temperature in Fahrenheit, rounded to 1 decimal place\r\n...\r\n\r\n"]
