[100.974452, "o", "Done! Here's what was completed:\r\n\r\n✅ **Created failing tests:**\r\n- `/workspace/hello-helix/package.json` — test script configured\r\n- `/workspace/hello-helix/tests/convert.test.js` — three temperature conversion tests:\r\n  - `toFahrenheit(0) === 32`\r\n  - `toCelsius(212) === 100`\r\n  - `toCelsius(98.6) ≈ 37.0`\r\n\r\n✅ **Tests are failing** — Module `../bin/convert.js` does not exist (as required)\r\n\r\n✅ **Issue claimed and closed:**\r\n- Issue ID: `hello-helix-2d27e2f5`\r\n- Title: \"Write failing tests for temperature conversion\"\r\n- Status: **closed**\r\n\r\n"]
